OL,11,G2300FJane McDonald: Lost in Japan
OL,12,     GIn 'Japan's Kitchen', Osaka, Jane
OL,13,     Gtakes a food tour that includes
OL,14,     Gthe best katsu that Osaka has to
OL,15,     Goffer. She also visits the
OL,16,     Gdowntown Dontonbori district
OL,17,     Gwhich reminds her of Manchester.
